# Mole Purge Paths - Auto-discovered project directories
# Edit this file to customize, or run: mo purge --paths
# Add one path per line (supports ~ for home directory)

# IMPORTANT: NEVER add active project or workspace roots here:
#   REMOVED: ~/dev / ~/dev/* (Contains active project code, venvs, LaunchAgent scripts)
#   REMOVED: ~/.config       (Contains active configuration files!)
